    <img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/c26e6efbc55697d43b123baf71e267f651feff7c.png" class="thumbnail onebox-avatar" width="400" height="400">

<h3><a href="https://github.com/frontity/frontity-embedded-proof-of-concept" target="_blank" rel="noopener">frontity/frontity-embedded-proof-of-concept</a></h3>

<p>PoC of the Embedded mode for Frontity sites. Contribute to frontity/frontity-embedded-proof-of-concept development by creating an account on GitHub.</p>


  </article>
  <div class="onebox-metadata">
    
    
  </div>
  <div style="clear: both"></div>
</aside>

<p>By implementing Frontity in this mode any RSS feed that you have in WordPress will work just fine.</p>
<p>Hope this helps</p>
